WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.330
You're not being ignored. You're being filtered.

00:00:03.330 --> 00:00:08.420
It filters anything that matches a known pattern. That's how it survives an infinite feed.

00:00:08.420 --> 00:00:15.930
Pattern interruption is the deliberate break, the half second something looks different enough to earn a second glance.

00:00:15.930 --> 00:00:21.500
Look at your last five posts. Same layout. Same tone. Same colors.

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:28.130
The brain already learned to skip them before reading a word. Break one pattern on purpose.

00:00:28.130 --> 00:00:32.070
If it looks like everything else, it gets seen like nothing.

00:00:32.067 --> 00:00:34.551
Perception and attention intelligence.

00:00:34.551 --> 00:00:42.234
If you want more of this, one breakdown lands in your inbox every week. Free, at arstrategists.com.
